at low wv: (Tb44/Tb43) > (Tb33/Tb34)
at high wv: (Tb44/Tb43) < (Tb33/Tb34)



(Tb44/Tb43) > (Tb33/Tb34) = good
44*34 > 33*43

44*34 / 33*43 > 1  = good

44*34 / 33*43 < 1  = bad

